{"sn14.38:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 14.38 ","sn14.38:0.2":"4. Catutthavagga ","sn14.38:0.3":"Dutiyasamanabrahmanasutta ","sn14.38:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn14.38:1.2":"“Catasso ima, bhikkhave, dhatuyo. ","sn14.38:1.3":"Katama catasso? ","sn14.38:1.4":"Pathavidhatu, apodhatu, tejodhatu, vayodhatu. ","sn14.38:1.5":"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samana va brahmana va imasam catunnam dhatunam samudayanca atthangamanca assadanca adinavanca nissarananca yathabhutam nappajananti …pe… ","sn14.38:1.6":"(vittharetabbam) ","sn14.38:1.7":"pajananti …pe… ","sn14.38:1.8":"sayam abhinna sacchikatva upasampajja viharanti”ti. ","sn14.38:1.9":"Navamam. "}